svg.title: Artboard 3
svg.text: MOTIVATIONSAmy is new to the world of design, and is currently gathering everything possible to help her.Typically, she downloads an image or takes a screenshot, and then she stores these on hercomputer. She’s used Pinterest before, but not for work. She likes being able to pull up thesite anywhere, but organizing the content isn’t the easiest. For notes, she defers to pen andpaper. It helps her remember things, but Amy often forgets to take the note pad with her whenshe leaves the house.
“Right now my computer can’t take all the images I’m trying to save. I need a simple way to capture and refer back to this stuff.”
